sequenceDiagram
    participant AI as AI Platform
    participant Write as Write Tool
    participant Hook as update-manifest.mjs
    participant Manifest as docs/manifest.json
    participant Config as config/doc-types.mjs
    
    AI->>Write: Write ARC-001-REQ-v1.0.md
    Write->>Hook: PostToolUse event<br/>(file path + content)
    Hook->>Hook: Parse filename<br/>extractDocType()
    Hook->>Config: Lookup type metadata<br/>DOC_TYPES["REQ"]
    Config-->>Hook: {category: "Discovery",<br/>name: "Requirements"}
    Hook->>Manifest: Read current manifest
    Manifest-->>Hook: JSON object
    Hook->>Hook: Find project 001<br/>or create if missing
    Hook->>Hook: Add/update document entry:<br/>{path, title, category,<br/>documentId}
    Hook->>Manifest: Write updated manifest
    Hook-->>AI: Continue execution
